<h3>If you log in, you can set templates as 'Favourites'.</h3>

<div class="tipText">Simply click on the star icon next to any templates of interest.  The star icons, however, will
not appear until you log in.</div>

<br/><br/>

<div align="center"><img src="tips/images/tip2a.png" class="img"/></div>

<br/><br/>

<div class="tipText">All templates you have marked will be displayed on the "Favourite Template" page in MyMine.</div>

